data.description: OPEN HOUSE SUNDAY 1-3!! PRICE IMPROVEMENT!! This beautiful Victorian style home sits on 4.82 acres.  Gorgeous woodwork throughout, 3 bedrooms, 2 full remodeled baths, updated kitchen with cherry cabinets, hardwood floors, living room fireplace, and more!  Detached 2 car garage, fenced in yard, barn with stables and water, fenced in pasture with electric fence, additional outbuilding for storage or a chicken coop.   This home is just ready for a new owner!
